metadata.name: 2 5 Travasol Amino Acid Injection With Electrolytes In 10 Dextrose 0 25 g mL Solution

clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: L phenylalanine may be helpful in some with depression It may also be useful in the treatment of vitiligo There is some evidence that L phenylalanine may exacerbate tardive dyskinesia in some schizophrenic patients and in some who have used neuroleptic drugs

contraindications.disease: L phenylalanine will exacerbate symptoms of phenylketonuria if used by phenylketonurics L phenylalanine was reported to exacerbate tardive dyskinesia when used by some with schizophrenia
contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Used by the brain to produce Norepinephrine a chemical that transmits signals between nerve cells and the brain keeps you awake and alert reduces hunger pains functions as an antidepressant and helps improve memory
